### Registering INSERT_UNORDERED_LIST_COMMAND Handler

Source: https://github.com/facebook/lexical/blob/main/packages/lexical-list/README.md

This snippet demonstrates how to register a command handler for inserting an unordered list using the $insertList function. It's a common pattern for integrating list functionality into custom Lexical plugins.

```typescript
import { $insertList } from '@lexical/list';
import { COMMAND_PRIORITY_LOW } from 'lexical';

// ... inside a plugin registration 
editor.registerCommand(INSERT_UNORDERED_LIST_COMMAND, () => {
    $insertList(editor, 'bullet');
    return true;
}, COMMAND_PRIORITY_LOW);

```

