### Dispatching INSERT_UNORDERED_LIST_COMMAND from a Toolbar Button

Source: https://github.com/facebook/lexical/blob/main/packages/lexical-list/README.md

This code shows how to dispatch the INSERT_UNORDERED_LIST_COMMAND from a UI element, such as a toolbar button. Clicking the button triggers the command, which can then be handled by a registered command listener.

```typescript
